Aquatic Druid	KEY:Druid Archetype ~ Aquatic Druid		CATEGORY:Archetype	TYPE:Archetype.DruidArchetype.DruidWoodlandStride.DruidTracklessStep.DruidNaturesLure.DruidVenomImmunity.DruidThousandFaces.DruidWildShape						PRECLASS:1,Druid=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Druid Archetype ~ Aquatic Druid],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.DruidWoodlandStride,TYPE.DruidTracklessStep,TYPE.DruidNaturesLure,TYPE.DruidVenomImmunity,TYPE.DruidThousandFaces,TYPE.DruidWildShape]								DESC:Shepherds of the lakes and seas, aquatic druids guard ecosystems ranging from shallows streams to deep ocean trenches, ministering to their residents and communing with the tides.																																	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Wild Empathy ~ Aquatic Druid	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Aquatic Adaptation ~ Aquatic Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=2	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Natural Swimmer ~ Aquatic Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=3	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Resist Oceans Fury ~ Aquatic Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=4	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Wild Shape ~ Aquatic Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=6	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Seaborn ~ Aquatic Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=9	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Deep Diver ~ Aquatic Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=13	COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.98
Arctic Druid	KEY:Druid Archetype ~ Arctic Druid		CATEGORY:Archetype	TYPE:Archetype.DruidArchetype.DruidWoodlandStride.DruidTracklessStep.DruidNaturesLure.DruidVenomImmunity.DruidThousandFaces.DruidWildShape						PRECLASS:1,Druid=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Druid Archetype ~ Arctic Druid],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.DruidWoodlandStride,TYPE.DruidTracklessStep,TYPE.DruidNaturesLure,TYPE.DruidVenomImmunity,TYPE.DruidThousandFaces,TYPE.DruidWildShape]								DESC:An arctic druid watches over the stark landscape of the far frozen reaches of the world, tending the stunted and rugged life that ekes out its survival in the least habitable climes.																																ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Arctic Native ~ Artic Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=2	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Icewalking ~ Artic Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=3	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Arctic Endurance ~ Artic Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=4	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Wild Shape ~ Artic Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=6	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Snowcaster ~ Artic Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=9	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Flurry Form ~ Artic Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=13																	COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.98
Blight Druid	KEY:Druid Archetype ~ Blight Druid		CATEGORY:Archetype	TYPE:Archetype.DruidArchetype.DruidThousandFaces.DruidVenomImmunity.DruidTracklessStep.DruidResistNaturesLure.DruidWildEmpathy								PRECLASS:1,Druid=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Druid Archetype ~ Blight Druid],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.DruidThousandFaces,TYPE.DruidVenomImmunity,TYPE.DruidTracklessStep.DruidResistNaturesLure.DruidWildEmpathy]													DESC:The devoted servants of nature corrupted, ruined, and destroyed, blight druids are the caretakers of lands ravaged by natural disaster. While some are devoted to reforming and reclaiming lands despoiled by the ravages of civilization, others seek out the more rapacious violence inherent in nature and feed the creeping rot and decay that brings an end to all things.	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Nature Bond ~ Blight Druid|Vermin Empathy ~ Blight Druid	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Miasma ~ Blight Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=5	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Blightblooded ~ Blight Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=9	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Plaguebearer ~ Blight Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=13																																									COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.98
Cave Druid		KEY:Druid Archetype ~ Cave Druid		CATEGORY:Archetype	TYPE:Archetype.DruidArchetype.DruidClassSkills.DruidNatureSense.DruidTracklessStep.DruidNatureBond.DruidWildEmpathy.DruidResistNaturesLure.DruidWildShape.DruidWoodlandStride	PRECLASS:1,Druid=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Druid Archetype ~ Cave Druid],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.DruidClassSkills,TYPE.DruidNatureSense,TYPE.DruidTracklessStep,TYPE.DruidNatureBond,TYPE.DruidWildEmpathy,TYPE.DruidResistNaturesLure,TYPE.DruidWildShape,TYPE.DruidWoodlandStride]	DESC:Far from the green fields of the world above lies a lightless expanse beneath the surface. This darkling fairyland is not without beauty and natural wonders of its own, and a few druids seek to preserve this hidden realm and purge it of the fell horrors that creep up from below.																ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Cavesense ~ Cave Druid|Nature Bond ~ Cave Druid|Wild Empathy ~ Cave Druid	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Tunnelrunner ~ Cave Druid|PREVARGTEQ:DruidLVL,2	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Lightfoot ~ Cave Druid|PREVARGTEQ:DruidLVL,3	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Resist Subterranean Corruption ~ Cave Druid|PREVARGTEQ:DruidLVL,4	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Wild Shape ~ Cave Druid|PREVARGTEQ:DruidLVL,6																					COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.99
Desert Druid	KEY:Druid Archetype ~ Desert Druid		CATEGORY:Archetype	TYPE:Archetype.DruidArchetype.DruidWoodlandStride.DruidTracklessStep.DruidResistNaturesLure.DruidWildShape.DruidVenomImmunity.DruidThousandFaces					PRECLASS:1,Druid=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Druid Archetype ~ Desert Druid],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.DruidWoodlandStride,TYPE.DruidTracklessStep,TYPE.DruidResistNaturesLure,TYPE.DruidWildShape,TYPE.DruidVenomImmunity,TYPE.DruidThousandFaces]							DESC:Not all climates are verdant paradises, but even in the sere deserts there is life-though often hidden from the sun and rarely friendly-and raw, desolate beauty. Here desert druids come to pay homage, protect and maintain the few habitable locales, and witness nature's majesty in all its burning, merciless glory.										ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Desert Native ~ Desert Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=2	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Sandwalker ~ Desert Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=3	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Desert Endurance ~ Desert Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=4	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Wild Shape ~ Desert Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=6	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Shaded Vision ~ Desert Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=9	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dunemeld ~ Desert Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=13														COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.99
Jungle Druid	KEY:Druid Archetype ~ Jungle Druid		CATEGORY:Archetype	TYPE:Archetype.DruidArchetype.DruidWoodlandStride.DruidTracklessStep.DruidResistNaturesLure.DruidWildShape.DruidThousandFaces									PRECLASS:1,Druid=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Druid Archetype ~ Jungle Druid],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.DruidWoodlandStride,TYPE.DruidTracklessStep,TYPE.DruidResistNaturesLure,TYPE.DruidWildShape,TYPE.DruidThousandFaces]											DESC:The fecund jungles of the equatorial regions are rich in life and ancient tradition; druidical guardians of sacred pools, elder trees, and trembling volcanoes watch over crumbling temples and the inevitable reclamation of lost civilizations by the beating heart of nature untamed.																ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Jungle Guardian ~ Jungle Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=2	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Woodland Stride ~ Jungle Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=3	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Torrid Endurance ~ Jungle Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=4	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Wild Shape ~ Jungle Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=6	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Verdant Sentinel ~ Jungle Druid|PRECLASS:1,Druid=13																										COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.100
