# Desert Druid
Desert Native					KEY:Desert Native ~ Desert Druid			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArchetypeDruid.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.DruidWoodlandStride																																																																									DESC:At 2nd level, a desert druid gains a bonus on Initiative checks and Knowledge (geography), Perception, Stealth, and Survival checks equal to 1/2 her druid level in desert terrain, and she cannot be tracked in such environments. This ability replaces woodland stride.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.99
Sandwalker						KEY:Sandwalker ~ Desert Druid				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArchetypeDruid.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.DruidTracklessStep																																																																									DESC:At 3rd level, a desert druid suffers no penalty to speed or on Acrobatics or Stealth checks when moving through sandy or desert terrain. This ability replaces trackless step.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.99
Desert Endurance					KEY:Desert Endurance ~ Desert Druid			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArchetypeDruid.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.DruidResistNaturesLure																																																																									DESC:At 4th level, a desert druid ignores the effects of a hot climate as if using endure elements. She also has a reduced need to eat and drink, as if wearing a ring of sustenance (though normal sleep is still required). This ability replaces resist nature's lure.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.99
Wild Shape						KEY:Wild Shape ~ Desert Druid				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArchetypeDruid.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.DruidWildShape					DEFINE:NoPlantShape|1																																																																		DESC:A desert druid gains this ability at 6th level, except that her effective druid level for the ability is equal to her druid level - 2. A desert druid cannot use wild shape to adopt a plant form. At 10th level she can assume the form of a Small or Medium vermin, at 12th level a Tiny or Large vermin, and at 14th level a Diminutive or Huge vermin. This effect functions as beast shape IV (treating the vermin as an animal to determine its ability and natural armor modifiers).																																																																																			ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Druid Wild Shape|Druid Wild Shape Progression|Druid Wild Shape Times																																																BONUS:VAR|DruidWildShape|-2																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.99
